      "height": 200,
      "text": "processContent API\n\n┌─────────────────┐\n│ DLP Policies     │\n│ • Credit Cards   │\n│ • SSN / PII      │\n│ • API Keys       │\n│ • Custom SITs    │\n└─────────────────┘\n\nClientSecretCredential\n(multi-tenant app)",
